Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,妈咪\NMum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,心是黑暗的森林\NTHE HEART IS A DARK FOREST
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,让门开着\NLeave it open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\NMorning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你何时到家的\NWhen did you get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎没睡上 马上要进行预演了\NI hardly got any sleep, and the rehearsal starts soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底为何回来\NWhy did you come at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我多待十五分钟吗\NDo I get 15 more minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 十分钟\NAlright, ten minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种采用传统养蜂方式的天然产品\NThis is a natural product from traditional beekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,由于其天然的粘稠性\NBecause of its natural consistency...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,蜂蜜不适合12个月以下的婴儿\Nhoney isn't suitable for infants under 12 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 小天使\NHello, little angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我能用洗手间吗 - 当然 你想用多久都行\NCan I go to the bathroom now? - Sure. As long as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑 小马驹 快跑\NRun, pony, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢\NThat's dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了 - 一切都很好\NWhat happened? - Everything alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 求你了 别\NNo, please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你能用两个勺子做这个吗\NCan you do that, can you make both spoons stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞎了吗\NAre you blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 你把汤匙放在眼皮上\NEy, you've got spoons on your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我看起来漂亮吗 - 我想有些大\NDo I look pretty? - I think it's a little too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,背后还没拉上\NIt's not closed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去坐到你的椅子上\NGo sit on your chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我想过去陪你 - 好极了\NI wanted to come with you tonight. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不吗 - 不是 当然好\NNo? - Yes, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有计划久待 演奏完离开\NI didn't plan to stay long, just play, then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我要过来吗\NBecause I want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,胡扯 昨天在理查兹举办了派对\NNonsense! They had a party at Richards yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有受邀请但因为提洛要去\NI wasn't invited, but still went because of Thilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是提洛\NWhy Thilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为昨晚是提洛举办的宴会\NThilo gave a dinner party last night at Richards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 我不清楚\NReally? I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么一到星期五你就很烦人 - 因为我总是惹人厌烦\NYou are always tired on Friday. - I'm ALWAYS tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么提洛要举办派对\NWhy did Thilo hold the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要咖啡吗\NCoffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,卖掉了许多画作\NSold lots of his paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人简直了\NThose people were awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我能清洁你的小提琴吗 - 好啊 我的女儿\NDad, can I clean your violin? - Yes, my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,尤尔根送来他的问候\NJuergen sends his regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不会把\NNever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的 “替我向玛丽问好，她过得怎样”等等\NYes, "Say hi to Marie, how is she" and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我在男厕所 和乔纳森有过愉快对话\NLater I had a nice talk with Jonathan in the men's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,仍旧是谈论音乐 还是流行的东西\NIs this still about music, or just this pop thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,流行\NPop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我想早点回家 好和你一起用早餐\NI wanted to come home early tomorrow, to have breakfast with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,或者可以去散步\NOr maybe we could take a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈能照看孩子们\NYour mother could have the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚问她 请求她明天来照顾孩子们\NI asked her to look after them tonight. - Then ask her to do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,去散步吗 - 是 或者聊天 天啊鬼知道要做什么\NTake a walk? - Yes, or talking or God knows what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这两个小天使\NYou little angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你牙齿上有东西\NThere's something on your tooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,显得很愚蠢 - 明显吗\NIt'll be totally stupid. - Or great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,算了\NWhatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,玩得开心 - 开心？该付房租了\NHave fun! - Fun? It's to pay the rent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再想要了\NI don't want it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你也并不想要\NYou don't want it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别自说自话 - 我是说真的\NSpeak for yourself. - It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要什么\NWhat do YOU want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要你负起责任来 - 那好啊\NI want you to want it too. - Then everything's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不付房租会发生什么\NWhat happens if you don't pay your rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那么在某个时候你们就必须要搬走\NThen you have to move at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,莱昂尼 你在做什么\NLeonie, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我把我的洋娃娃放进了爸爸的提琴箱里 他还没有\NI put my doll into Dad's case and he hasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,发现\Nnoticed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你们认为这样行啊\NDo you think it'll work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,最好再离电视机远一点\NBetter leave the TV alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在它们播完前回来\NI'm back before they've finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,无论对方说什么都不要开门 水在餐桌上\NAnd don't open the door, whatever they say. Water is on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我很快回来\NI'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯\NThomas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯\NThomas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 托马斯刚来过没\NSorry, didn't Thomas just came in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽 这是我们的儿子保罗\NMarie, that's our son Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想给我们的儿子取名保罗 你却不愿意\NI wanted to name our son Paul, but you didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,坐好\NSit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你进庭院去 好吗\NAnd you go into the garden, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\NMarie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\NMarie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是要我冷静 我有种知觉 你随口糊弄我\NYou always calm me down. I have a feeling, you say it doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你错了 我没有打电话\NYou're wrong, I didn't phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天 我不会再有任何感觉\NOne day, I won't have feelings anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉就像在精神上 依赖着其他人的谎言\NI'll feel like being on psychotropics, dependent on other peoples lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么脱身 - 玛丽 别取闹 我必须要工作\NHow do I get off? - Marie, don't flip. I HAVE to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我也应当工作 - 我们一定会处理好这些的\NPerhaps I have to work too. - We'll have to organise it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要处理好\NI'll have to organise it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须离开了 - 我也是\NI have to go. - Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NStay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 你做的很出色\NCome on, you're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就到头了 小的孩子将上幼稚园了\NIt'll be over soon, the little one will be in the nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你 其他女人都能做到的\NWe need you. Other women can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那我不算是一个女人 - 你是里面最出色的\NThen I'm not a woman. - You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了\NI'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁在那里吗\NIs anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊 我们在\NYes, we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\NOf course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你去了哪里\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,公车没来 - 你骑的车\NThe bus didn't come... - You cycled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我收拾了屋子\NI tidied the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,来\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,过来吧孩子们\NAre you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我能接电话吗 - 不能\NCan I go to the phone? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,估计是外婆 她想知道是否该过来\NBet it's Grandma. She wants to know if she should come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\NAlright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你听见你爸爸怎么说的 外婆明天过来\NYou heard what your father said. Grandma's coming tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我问问她 - 别去\NI'll ask her. - That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 - 真是够了\NHello? - That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,莱昂尼\NLeonie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 妈妈 喂\NHello mum? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 妈妈 - 我在\NHello mum. - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你挂掉了电话吗 - 什么\NDid you drop the receiver? - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚打给我\NYou just phoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗 这真是热情的接待\NAre you crazy? That's a warm-hearted reception!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点 我就问一下 - 是那样吗 你和我说话的方式…\NCalm down. I just asked a question. - Really, the way you talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NWait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 要等什么 - 我回头打给你\NWait, for what? - I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该过来还是不 - 之后再说 拜\NShould I come or not? - Then do something else, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,电话里是谁\NWho was on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘记了关掉厨房的煤气\NYou forgot to switch off the gas in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,电话里是谁\NWho was on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆\NGrandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆\NGrandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆\NGrandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 莱昂尼\NGood night, Leonie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们并排坐在池塘边\NWe sat together at the pond...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,艾略特 我还有月亮\NElliot, me and the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有很多话谈\NWe had lots to talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,莱昂尼 告诉过最早是谁打来电话\NLeonie, tell me who phoned earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道不是外婆 我跟她谈过\NI know it wasn't grandma, I talked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 莱昂尼 告诉我\NCome on, Leonie, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当小鸟看见鸭子\NWhen the little bird saw the duck...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你在伤心吗\NAre you sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我在发愁\NI'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.48,0:21:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你没把洋娃娃放进爸爸的提琴箱\NIf you hadn't put your doll in Dad's case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的 妈妈 爸爸向汉斯借了一把小提琴\NNo problem, Mum, Dad borrowed a violin from Hanns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不要跟他说是我告诉你的 - 什么\NBut don't tell him that I told you. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸早些时候在电话里跟我讲的\NIt was Dad on the phone today earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是 - 我们中午的时候也说过\NI thought so. - We also spoke at lunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么没有告诉我\NWhy didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗 现在生我的气 即使不关我的事\NSee? Now you're cross with me, even though it's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,胡说八道\NNonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 - 他说了什么\NOuch! - What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.92,0:22:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他发现了我的洋娃娃在提琴箱里\NThat he found my doll in the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有生气 因为他从汉斯那儿借到一把提琴\Nand that he wasn't angry, because he could borrow a violin from Hanns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还有呢\NAnd?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他问我们在做什么\NHe asked what we were doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有呢 - 没有了 吃了意大利面\NAnd? - Nothing. Eating spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他讲我不应该告诉你他打来电话\NHe said I shouldn't tell you that he phoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\NI see!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很快我们就要去度假喽\NSoon we're all going on holiday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信他吗\NAnd you believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为你爸让你对我撒谎这是对的\NI don't think it's right that your father told you to lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该停止争吵\NYou should stop arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我感到抱歉\NI'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你有爱人吗\NDo you have a lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.20,0:24:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样问\NYou think you can just ask like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样 - 疯子\NSo what? - Madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.04,0:24:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别隐瞒\NDon't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.98,0:24:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗 - 快告诉我\NAre you crazy? - Just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.96,0:24:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 - 不 我不想知道\NAlright. - No, I don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽 我爱你 别这样看着我\NMarie, I love you. Don't look at me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,完了 - 真的吗\Nthese things happen. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.64,0:24:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你说过 人和人是有所不同的\NBut you said, this is one and the other one is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.04,0:24:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫多疑\NIt's called paranoia.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.16,0:24:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,混淆了现实和恐惧 你需要专业的帮助\NTo mix up reality with fear. You need professional help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.24,0:24:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一位心理医生或者什么东西像这样\NA psychiatrist or something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.20,0:24:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,最好是和我上床\NBetter sleep with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.32,0:25:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,最好是和我上床\NBetter sleep with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.52,0:25:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,最好是和我上床\NBetter sleep with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.48,0:26:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 在吗\NYes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.64,0:26:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 - 我在\NHello? - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.48,0:26:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\NListen!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.84,0:26:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍在那里吗 - 是\NAre you still there? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.76,0:26:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得吗\NDo you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.41,0:26:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 但是我快没时间了\NOf course, but I don't have time right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.68,0:26:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 - 你还好吗\NSorry... - How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.36,0:26:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我还好\NYes, I feel just great...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.32,0:26:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 玛丽 我明天回来 - 好的 明天是\NListen, Marie, I'll come by tomorrow. - Yes, tomorrow is...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.32,0:26:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,明天很好\NTomorrow is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.72,0:26:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吗 - 是的\NIs that okay? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.60,0:27:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到吗 - 能\NCan you make it? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.28,0:27:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要是\NWhat if...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.44,0:27:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到\NI don't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.00,0:28:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,午夜时间 你们在这里做什么\NWhat are you doing here in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.44,0:28:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来自精神急症科 能和你谈谈吗\NWe are from the psychiatric emergency service. Could we talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.52,0:28:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 孩子们已经睡了 - 我们希望亲眼确认\NNo way, my children are asleep. - We'd like to see this for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.56,0:28:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫来电话说你威胁要自杀\NYour husband phoned and said you threatened to kill yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.08,0:28:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好 看向我\NThere, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.28,0:28:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝醉了吗\NAre you drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.16,0:28:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,每个德国人晚上都会喝一杯\NEvery German has a drink in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.16,0:28:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,两个小孩都睡着了 脉搏正常\NBoth children are asleep. Pulse is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.88,0:28:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是诽谤\NThat's scandalous!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.76,0:28:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我感到抱歉 但这是我们职责所在\NI'm sorry, but we were informed and it's our duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.88,0:28:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这简直是侮辱\NThis is so humiliating.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.52,0:28:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.00,0:28:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 如果你需要帮助或支援 请联系我们\NListen, if you need help or support, please call us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.56,0:28:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么麻烦是不能解决的\NThere's nothing wrong with having a problem one can't solve...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.64,0:29:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫就有一个麻烦 还不小\NMy husband has a problem, not a small one...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.08,0:29:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他听上去很绝望 他不知道该做些什么\NHe sounded desperate. He didn't know what else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.84,0:29:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该自己回来 没人能强迫他\NHe should have come himself. - No one can force him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.36,0:29:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不太好 但能应付\NI'm not great, but I cope.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.04,0:29:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我有朋友 并不需要你们\NI have friends. I don't need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.64,0:29:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 如果还有\NWell, if there is anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.00,0:29:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那混蛋\NThat asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.40,0:30:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,中央车站\NCENTRAL STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.72,0:31:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯\NThomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.92,0:31:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我怀孕了怎么办\NWhat if I am pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.04,0:31:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,说这个太早了 - 但是如果呢\NIt's too early to say. - But if?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.96,0:31:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会打掉它\NThen we'll have an abortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.44,0:32:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.16,0:32:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 安娜\NHello, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.64,0:32:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要进来吗 他不在这里\NDo you want to come in? He isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.28,0:32:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.12,0:33:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你接着去睡觉 好吗\NThen you go to sleep, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.04,0:33:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,绿茶总尝起来一股青草味\NGreen tea always tastes just green.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.40,0:33:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕我伤害你吗\NAre you afraid I'll hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.12,0:33:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以尝试\NYou can try...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.44,0:34:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.32,0:34:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你知道为何我不再联络了\NNow you know why I didn't call anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.64,0:34:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我常常想起你 一直是\NI've often thought about you. The whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.72,0:34:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他也说过 - 噢 谢谢\NI talked to him too... - Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.88,0:34:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是错的 我们的方式\NIt was wrong... the way we...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.20,0:34:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我又忙于孩子 还有巡展\NAnd I was so busy with the child, and being on tour...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.88,0:34:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 孩子占据了你们很大一部分 - 是的 完全是\NYes, children take a lot out of you. - Yes, totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.64,0:34:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还有艺术品 服装 每件事\NAnd the artwork, the costumes... Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.52,0:34:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们又有了舞蹈家\NAnd they have dancers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.84,0:34:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过他们吗\NHave you met them?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.12,0:34:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,打断一下\NTo break off...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.16,0:34:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不是仅和你 那时候和任何人相处\Nnot only with you, but with everybody in that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.32,0:34:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,都像在自罚\Nthat was like self-punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.04,0:35:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没有成为过一个团体的一部分 也从没这么快乐过\NI never was part of a group before, and never so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.36,0:35:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢\NAnd now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.60,0:35:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你快乐吗\NAre you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.72,0:35:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴我们正交谈着\NI'm glad we're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.80,0:35:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有些闷热\NIt's kind of sticky in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.48,0:35:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.52,0:35:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该在白天见面谈话\NWe should meet during the day and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.52,0:35:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,今天时间太短了\NToday it's all a little too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.64,0:35:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 我感到抱歉\NSure, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.32,0:35:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以给我打电话 - 好 我很乐意\NYou can call me. - Yes, I like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.88,0:35:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,明天 我们休假 然后 - 我得离开了 只是想着看看你\NTomorrow, we're off, but then... - I'm going, just wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.20,0:35:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有些遗憾 真的\NA pity, but sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.16,0:35:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我有落下一把小提琴在这里吗 - 没\NDid I leave a violin case here? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.80,0:35:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你来时空手就行 告诉我\NYou had nothing when you came. Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.88,0:36:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你又开始演奏了吗 - 整天都在\NAre you playing again? - All day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.96,0:36:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一切顺利\NAll the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.40,0:36:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 拜\NYes, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.28,0:36:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我一回来就立刻联络你 - 好的\NI'll call immediately on my return. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.56,0:36:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,拜 - 拜\NBye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.96,0:36:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,拜 拜 - 拜托 关上门\NBye, bye... - Come on, close the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.00,0:37:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,请到沃尔德克堡\NCastle Waldeck, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.16,0:37:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这就走\NOff we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.80,0:38:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来不错 - 恩\NYou look great... - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.32,0:38:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 - 什么\NGreat. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.04,0:38:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快 我们走吧\NCome on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.40,0:38:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知为什么感觉很蠢\NI feel stupid somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.96,0:38:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我累得要死 我想就这么待着\NI'm dead tired. I'm staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.72,0:38:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,让保姆走吧 我们仍然会付她薪水\NDrop the babysitter off, we'll still pay her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.60,0:38:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 别 玛丽 - 不要逼我\NOh no, Marie... - Don't push me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.80,0:38:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我们愉快地用早餐 好吗\NWe'll have a lovely breakfast tomorrow, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.56,0:38:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我该让你在这下车吗\NShould I drop you off here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.24,0:38:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 谢谢你\NYes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.92,0:39:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我该返回 - 我已经关掉了计程器\NOr should I go back... - I already switched off the meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.12,0:40:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.96,0:40:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我捡到一把乐师的乐器\NI've got an instrument for the musicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.04,0:40:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要怎么进去\NHow do I get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.16,0:40:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,从门走\NThrough the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.12,0:41:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.80,0:41:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在轮到你了\NNow it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.48,0:41:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沃\NWhoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.00,0:41:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 园丁让我进来了\NSorry, the gardener let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.36,0:41:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到一把叫提昂尼奥的乐师的小提琴\NI have a violin for a musician of the "Trioneo".
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.36,0:42:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 我认为这是一起抢劫案\NPhew, and I thought it was a hold-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.72,0:42:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你不会失望 - 我希望你捡到一套衣服\NI hope you aren't disappointed. - I hope you've got a costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.24,0:42:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,从这下去 在左边就是乐师们的更衣室\NDown there, to the left is the musicians' dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.96,0:42:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都在吗 - 不 只有他\NIs everybody there already? - No. Just him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.20,0:42:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看看谁来了 - 还不赖\NThere you are! - Not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.60,0:42:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊\NIt's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.96,0:42:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我很快回来\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.96,0:43:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 真舒服\NOh yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.52,0:43:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小猫咪\NMy little pussycat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.38,0:43:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须离开了 赫尔穆特随时可能过来\NYou have to go, Helmut will be here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.64,0:43:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就让他来吧 米兹 总有一天\NJust let him come, Mietzi. One day...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.20,0:43:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天我们都会死\NOne day we'll all be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.56,0:43:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.60,0:43:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请进\NCome in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.28,0:43:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别弄出噪音 孩子们正在隔壁睡觉\NDon't make a racket, the children are sleeping next door today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.04,0:43:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有什么需要\NWhat else do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.00,0:43:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能给我一支烟吗\NMay I have a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.92,0:44:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她杀害了自己的孩子 - 玛丽亚 卡拉斯\NShe killed her own children. - Maria Callas?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.84,0:44:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,美狄亚\NMedea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.16,0:44:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,报复她的丈夫 他为了别的女人离开了她\NRevenge on her husband. He left her for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.40,0:44:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,十分正确\NQuite right!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.12,0:44:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,米兹\NMietzi...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.96,0:44:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍尔施米特吵醒我们了 - 这里没有鲍尔施米特啊\NBauerschmidt woke us up! - There's no Bauerschmidt here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.96,0:44:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚才从我们房间走过 - 胡说八道\NHe just walked through our room... - Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.16,0:44:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想要一杯热可可和一则故事 - 没有热可可\NWe want a hot chocolate and a story... - No hot chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.64,0:45:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意 我可以给你们读一则故事\NI can read you a story if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.12,0:45:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这两个孩子挨饿而无法入睡\N"The two children couldn't sleep because they were hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.84,0:45:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,又听见继母对父亲说的话\Nand had heard what the stepmother had said to the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.16,0:45:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,格雷特尔哭着对汉塞尔说\NGretel cried and said to Hansel:
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.20,0:45:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们完了\N"Now we're doomed."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.52,0:45:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但汉塞尔说道 别担心 格雷特尔 我会找到一条出路的\NBut Hansel said: "Don't worry, Gretel, I'll find a way out."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.76,0:45:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然后等到大人们睡着了\N"And when the grown-ups slept..."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.32,0:45:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 - 够了\NWhat? - Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.72,0:45:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样搅合\NDon't shuffle like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.40,0:45:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他在这里 我看见了 这一次\NHe was here. I saw him. This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.99,0:45:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别吼叫\NDon't shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.92,0:45:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看 那是鲍尔施米特 - 是啊\NSee? It WAS Bauerschmidt! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.80,0:45:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我要读下去吗 - 我一点也不在乎\NShall I read on? - I don't give a damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.44,0:45:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这只猩猩到底想干什么 - 你到底在说什么\NWhat does the ape want here? - Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.40,0:45:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,别瞒着我 别这样看我\NDon't lie to me. Not like that, not to my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.76,0:45:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.92,0:45:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.12,0:45:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 又是你 - 抱歉\NJesus, you again! - Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.80,0:45:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们睡不着 - 妈妈 鲍尔施米特来过\NThe children couldn't sleep. - Mum, Bauerschmidt was here...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.56,0:45:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然后赫尔穆特回来了 然后 - 是 是 是 是\Nand then Helmut came, and... - Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.72,0:46:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我要杀了他 然后你 然后我自己\NI'll kill him! And then you, and then myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.96,0:46:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗 够了 安静些 - 别跟我说这些\NAre you crazy? That's it, be quiet! - Don't tell me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.60,0:46:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听他有多疯狂 - 赫尔穆特 请你现在就离开\NYou can hear how crazy he is. - And Helmut, please leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.72,0:46:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再见到你\NI don't want to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.96,0:46:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这里除了我没别人 - 她在撒谎\NThere was no one here but me. - She's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.08,0:46:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这不关我事 好吗\NThis is none of my business, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.12,0:46:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不想知道 明白吗 - 是的 那好\NI want no part of that, is that clear? - Yes, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.84,0:46:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 就是这样了 我数到20然后你们就入睡\NSo, that's it. I count to 20 and then both of you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.36,0:46:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,1\NOne.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.52,0:46:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,2\NTwo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.88,0:46:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,3\NThree.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.32,0:46:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,4\NFour.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.88,0:46:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,5\NFive.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.96,0:46:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,6\NSix.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.40,0:46:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,7\NSeven.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.32,0:46:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,8\NEight.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.08,0:46:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,18\NEighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.16,0:46:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,19\NNineteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.92,0:46:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 这真是太好了\NThank you, that's very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.40,0:46:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己有两个孩子\NI've got two myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.40,0:46:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,年纪小一些\NA little younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.52,0:47:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你很想和他们躺一起吗\NYou really want to lie down with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.36,0:47:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不 今天不了 你有我可以穿的衣服吗\NNo, not today. Do you by any chance have a costume for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.12,0:47:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一整箱\NI've got a whole trunk full of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.64,0:47:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是 你不该看起来这么吸引人\NMost important, you shouldn't look attractive!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.80,0:47:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 - 玩开心\NThank you. - Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.24,0:47:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你能载我吗 - 发生什么了\NCan you pick me up? - What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.84,0:48:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我身上有很多精液\NThere was so much semen, it was all over me...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.88,0:48:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,洗不掉了 - 听上去糟透了 你去哪儿了\NAnd nothing to clean it off. - Sounds awful. Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.80,0:48:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,楼下的长椅上 在花园里\NDownstairs, on a bench. In the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.80,0:48:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你真脏\NYou pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.88,0:48:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他后来做了什么吗 - 不知道\NDo you know what he did then? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.48,0:48:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他脱下他的袜子替我擦脸\NHe took off his sock and cleaned my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.00,0:48:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要吐了\NI'm going to barf...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.60,0:48:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪了\NStrange...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.40,0:48:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这样\NI liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.72,0:48:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,留意只穿一只袜子的人 好吗\NLook out for someone who wears just one sock, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.24,0:49:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,汉斯\NHanns!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.12,0:50:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\NMarie?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.72,0:50:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿做什么\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.00,0:50:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯把他的小提琴落在家里 - 我知道\NThomas left his violin at home. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.84,0:50:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道你在这里吗 - 他不需要知道\NDoes he know that you're here? - He doesn't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.44,0:50:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 无所谓 你看上去不错\NYeah, whatever. You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.52,0:50:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 能给我一支烟吗\NThanks. Got a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.56,0:50:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你想等着托马斯吗\NDo you want to wait for Thomas?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.64,0:50:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要我去拿些喝的吗\NShall I get us something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.56,0:50:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我犯相思病了\NI think I'm lovesick.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.48,0:50:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真有趣 我还以为你不知道那是什么意思\NFunny, I thought you wouldn't know what it meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.44,0:50:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为你是蕾丝边 - 什么\NI always thought you were a lesbian. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.56,0:50:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.92,0:50:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾丝边就从不犯相思病吗\NAnd lesbians are never lovesick?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.44,0:50:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 管它的呢 你是吗\NDon't know, don't give a shit. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.48,0:50:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.72,0:51:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 不太清楚 为什么你这么说\NNot that I know, I don't know. Why do you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.88,0:51:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你看上去似乎不在乎\NWell, it looked like you didn't seem to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.80,0:51:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不在乎什么 - 好吧\NAbout what? - Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.60,0:51:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯和那个女人\NThomas and the women...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.08,0:51:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次听说\NFirst time I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.96,0:51:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 太明显了 每个人都知道\NWell, it was so obvious, everybody knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.80,0:51:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不知道 为什么你从没跟我说过\NI didn't. Why didn't you ever tell me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.36,0:51:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你了 我以为你是蕾丝边\NTold you, thought you were a lesbian.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.00,0:51:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,以为你们俩有某种交易 没人知道情况 我是说\NThought the two of you had some kind of a deal. Nobody knows, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.24,0:51:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,从没见过你和别的男人一起的时候 但是你也一定有性生活吧\NNever saw you with another man. But you must have had sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.20,0:51:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不 - 不什么\NNo! - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.20,0:51:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的结论啊\NWhat a conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.76,0:51:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一个男人对自己妻子不忠 所以她就必须变得性冷淡\NA man cheats on his wife, so she has to be frigid...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.48,0:51:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是蕾丝边\Nor a lesbian.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.92,0:51:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你清楚 我知道些什么吗\NYou know, what do I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.12,0:51:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是什么都知道 汉斯 - 是啊 我明白\NYou always know everything, Hanns. - Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.96,0:52:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小提琴在桌上\NThe violin is on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.08,0:53:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,1 2 3 4\NOne, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.76,0:53:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哎唷\NOuch!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.36,0:53:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道明天怎么去做\NDon't know how to do the thing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.92,0:53:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.20,0:53:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么办 - 你在说些什么\NI don't know how... - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.52,0:53:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕谈论我的问题 - 你是什么意思\NI'm afraid to talk about my problems. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.24,0:53:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须跟你父亲讲 参加试演 我做不到\NI have to talk to your father, what to play at the audition... I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.28,0:53:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然可以 - 我极度紧张\NSure you can! - I'm ULTRA stressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.44,0:53:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你也一样 但为什么 - 你要演奏什么\NI know, you are too, but why? - What will you play?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.00,0:53:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,柴可夫斯基\NTchaikovsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.85,0:53:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真消沉 - 我撤掉了\NHow low. - I cancel.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.44,0:53:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,废话 他讨厌柴可夫斯基 - 或许这还不算太坏\NNonsense, he hates Tchaikovsky! - Perhaps that's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.28,0:53:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,演奏巴赫 - 什么\NPlay Bach. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.40,0:53:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,奏鸣曲独奏 简单 我有极好的记录\NSolo Sonata! Simple! I've a great record.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.72,0:53:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不行 我宁可睡觉也不讨论这个\NNo, don't get it. I'd rather sleep than talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.23,0:53:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我很快把它拿来\NI'll fetch it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.08,0:53:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,别 我已经 我去沙发上睡了\NNo, I'm already de... I sleep on the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.72,0:53:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 会有成效的\NCome here, it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.20,0:53:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,让他谈论巴赫 他热爱于此\NLet him talk about Bach, he loves Bach.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.28,0:53:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 也许这样更好\NYes, maybe that's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.44,0:53:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 抱歉\NAbsolutely! Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.48,0:54:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我主耶稣\NJesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.72,0:54:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我在做梦 此刻请将我唤醒\NIf I'm dreaming, please wake me up now...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.72,0:55:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,当你问时 你已经认识到了真相\NYou recognise reality when you ask:
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.44,0:55:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是梦吗\NIs this a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.96,0:55:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在梦中你从不会问 我是否在做梦\NWhilst dreaming you never say: "Do I dream?"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.24,0:55:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在梦中一切只是发生着\NIn a dream everything just happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.20,0:55:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就像行人路过乞丐\Nlike pedestrians passing a beggar.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.32,0:55:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NOh God...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.44,0:55:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以叫我瓦伦汀\NYou can call me Valentin...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.92,0:55:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\NDad!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.12,0:55:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 陪我坐着 和我喝一杯\NCome, sit with me. Have a drink with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.44,0:55:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不好意思独自喝酒\NI'm embarrassed to drink alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.48,0:55:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就快开始了\NIt's about to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.88,0:55:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,焰火\NThe fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.08,0:55:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见了吗\NDid you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.28,0:55:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见什么了\NWhat did I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.60,0:55:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到一个金发女人 个子高高的 修长的腿\NI see a blonde woman, tall, straight legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.68,0:55:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,多情可人\Nand enough dramatic expression to break everyone's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.48,0:56:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 那是我 玛丽 - 玛丽\NDad, it's me, Marie. - Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.60,0:56:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你的女儿\NYour daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.08,0:56:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小猫\NKitten...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.56,0:56:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你\NLet me look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.80,0:56:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧 我的眼镜让我头疼\NYou see, my glasses give me a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.76,0:56:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你试图勾引我\NYou tried to hit on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.60,0:56:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的事 我想要观看焰火\NNo. I wanted to watch the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.84,0:56:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.08,0:56:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.36,0:56:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,吉赛尔在哪儿 你独自一人吗 - 糟糕的派对 对吗\NWhere is Giselle? Are you alone? - Terrible party, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.92,0:56:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么没有打给我 你人来汉堡的时候\NWhy don't you call me, when you're in Hamburg?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.92,0:56:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天得去萨尔茨堡\NI have to go to Salzburg tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.80,0:56:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你最后一次见孩子们是在 等等 在你的生日上\NLast time you saw the children, was... wait, at your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.16,0:56:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经上大学了吗\NAre they already at college?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.16,0:56:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,莱昂尼快上学前班 艾略特快上幼稚园\NLeonie will go to preschool soon, Elliot will go to nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.32,0:56:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就能够再次工作了\NThen you'll be able to work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.20,0:56:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你随时都可以回来\NYou know that you can come back anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.52,0:56:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯在试用期 我们随时可以撵走他\NThomas is on probation. We can get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.92,0:57:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样他爱好流行更多\NAnyhow he loves this pop thing a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.28,0:57:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你在暗示什么 - 你一直要比他优秀\NDad, what are you suggesting? - You've always been better than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.12,0:57:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没人配得上你\NNobody is good enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.88,0:57:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍然有练习吗 - 爸爸\NYou're still practising, aren't you? - Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.16,0:57:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯有别的女人 另一幢房子 孩子\NThomas has another woman. Another house, children...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.28,0:57:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,每样东西他都有两件 复制品 你懂吗\NHe has two of everything. A duplicate, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.76,0:57:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\NJesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.84,0:57:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你可以靠那些流行东西得到一大笔钱\NSo you can make a lot of money with that pop stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.68,0:57:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如今你可以袖手旁观 看那个蠢货度过他的余生\NNow can you watch that idiot spending the rest of his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.44,0:57:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,工作能让你得以维持\Nworking to keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.80,0:57:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好注意 美好生活\NGreat idea! Great life!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.00,0:57:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直告诉你他一无是处\NI always told you that he's a good for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.40,0:57:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我的心受伤了\NDad, my heart is wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.40,0:57:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,请安慰我\NPlease comfort me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.08,0:58:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\NCome!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.80,0:58:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不不知道我为何还在这里\NI don't know why I'm still here...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.36,0:58:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 那么回家去吧 小猫\NWell, then go home, kitten...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.08,0:58:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和他谈谈 -几时\NI want to talk with him! - When?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.96,0:58:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 现在吗\NHere? Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.16,0:58:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 - 没什么 一切总会好转\NWhat's wrong? - No, everything is alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.12,0:58:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我将重蹈妈妈的覆辙\NI'm going to have the same life as Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.00,0:58:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 但你对我来说太沉了\NSorry, but you're too heavy for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.72,0:58:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我将像她一样 抑郁地坐在屋里 吓唬孩子\NI'll be like her, sitting depressed at home, terrorising the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.84,0:58:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈是个病妇 你 有天赋 你有乐器\NYour mother is a sick woman. You... have talent. You have an instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.28,0:58:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈也一样\NSo did Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.48,0:59:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她抚养了两个孩子 她曾经可以拥有事业如果你让\NShe raised two kids. If you had done that, she could have had a career.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.48,0:59:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 亲爱的 你不清楚这事\NSorry, darling. You're confusing the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.40,0:59:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我遇见你妈时 我完全知道我想要什么 但她不是\NWhen I met your mother, I knew exactly what I wanted. She did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.72,0:59:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有胆量 你本可以支持她\NShe didn't dare. You could have supported her!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.48,0:59:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须顾及我自己 那时候才刚起步\NI had to look after myself. It was only the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.24,0:59:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而接着她有了一个孩子\NAnd then she had a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.20,0:59:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是你们俩有了一个孩子 那是我\NBoth of you had a child! That was ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.32,0:59:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 坐下来吧\NCome on, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.92,0:59:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要一起待着 看吧 是焰火\NWe still have so much time together. Look, the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.44,1:00:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\NMarie?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.76,1:00:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯 我要开始了\NThomas, I begin...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.84,1:00:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,赫尔穆特 你现在必须回家去了 - 是啊 是这样\NHelmut, you have to go home now! - Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.48,1:01:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们真棒 是吧\NThey are great, hm?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.44,1:02:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来 别跌倒了\NStand up! Don't fall...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.72,1:02:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么从这里出去 - 这里没有出口\NHow do I get out of here? - There is no way out.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.60,1:02:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字 - 乔纳森\NWhat's your name? - Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.80,1:03:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,乔纳森 抱紧我\NJonathan, hold me tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.12,1:03:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,乔纳森\NJonathan!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.52,1:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么回事 你想折磨我吗\NWhat's wrong? Do you want to wear me down?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.00,1:03:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你的所作所为\NAnd the way you look!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.84,1:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的袜子在哪儿\NAnd where is your sock?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.44,1:03:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 你喝醉了吗 - 你这混蛋\NWhat? Are you drunk? - You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.32,1:03:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我的人生做了什么\NWhat did you do to my life?!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.32,1:03:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我离开 - 玛丽\NNo, I'm leaving! - Marie!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.32,1:03:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你们俩会对你们的所作所为感到快乐 而且尿在彼此身上\NHope you'll both be happy with what you did, and piss on each other!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.44,1:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你不在家 孩子们在哪儿\NWhy aren't you home? Where are the children?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.28,1:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好像你很感兴趣似的 - 你妈和他们在一起吗\NAs if that would interest you THAT much! - Your mother is with them...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.20,1:04:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的闭嘴的\NShut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.00,1:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 我们能回到这个问题上吗 你妈妈有没有和他们在一起\NFine, we can go on talking like this. Is your mother with them?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.00,1:04:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只有他们俩\NThey are alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.68,1:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们睡着了而且再不会醒来\NThey sleep and will never wake up again.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.24,1:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而且在解决了你之后 我再自刎\NAnd after I'm through with you, I'll slash myself!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.76,1:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全疯了 我一个字都不敢相信\NYou are totally crazy! I don't believe a single word!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.32,1:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,再会 好吗 都结束了\NYes, bye, it's over...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.28,1:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子们\NMy little ones...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.52,1:04:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望他们依然安睡\NI hope they're still asleep...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.04,1:04:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 他们熟睡着\NSure. They're asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.24,1:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我一切都结束了\NTell me that it'll be over...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.36,1:04:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,说你爱我 跟我说一切都会好起来\NSay that you love me, tell me that everything will be fine...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.96,1:04:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哭 总是哭\NThe crying... Always the crying...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.44,1:05:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你总哭要怎么才说得清\NOne can't talk, if you always cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.52,1:05:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都一个样\NYou're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.68,1:05:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡巴玩意儿\NPenis!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.56,1:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\NYeah...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.16,1:05:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 这就是你所想的\NYeah, that's what you think.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.96,1:05:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你错了 亲爱的 你都错了\NBut you are wrong, my dear. All of you are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.84,1:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白 你无能为力\NYou don't understand. But you can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.68,1:05:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,它就在你体内 你被迫怀着它\NIt's inside of you! You're compelled to procreate...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.24,1:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,它胜过了你的理智 别人必须就要迁就着你\Nit's stronger than your intellect. One has to be careful with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.28,1:05:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有任何人问过我吗\NDid anybody ask me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.36,1:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有 我问过 - 然后我怎么说\NYes, I did! - And what did I say?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.36,1:05:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,操 妈的\NFuck, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.56,1:05:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想那样\NI didn't want that!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.04,1:05:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但那不重要了 那不是我的全部\NBut that doesn't matter. It wasn't about me at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.88,1:05:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你只想着你那愚蠢的浪漫 为人母的感觉\NYou just wanted your stupid romantic, motherly feelings!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.76,1:05:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,来 站起来 你必须控制住你自己\NCome, get up. You have to get hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.48,1:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我带孩子们度假 你也会有所好转\NI take the children with me on holiday, and you get better.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.16,1:06:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别从我身旁带走孩子 - 停止胡闹\NDon't take the children away from me. - Stop this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.60,1:06:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,去度假吧 到海边旅行 休息一下\NGo on holiday too, travel to the sea. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.60,1:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,带上女伴 萨布里娜怎么样\NTake a girlfriend. What about Sabrina?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.92,1:06:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没了 我什么都不想\NI've got nothing. I... I don't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.52,1:06:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,都结束了 是吗\NIt's over, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.52,1:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是他干的\NHe did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.92,1:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,林中房屋失火了\NThe forester's house is burning!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.96,1:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\NMarie?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.04,1:07:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来 不会有事的\NCome on, this won't lead to anything today.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.64,1:07:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝 我们提早拿到了报酬\NThank heavens that we got paid in advance!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.24,1:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她离开了 - 是吗 你送走她的吗\NShe's gone! - Well, you did send her away.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.16,1:07:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她那么愤怒\NShe was so angry...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.36,1:07:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 每天都是 当你有了自己的演奏会的时候 女人都这样\NYes, today of all days. When you had your concert. Typical woman!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.32,1:07:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,楼下有很多鬼魂\NUnder the stairs is a lot of spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.52,1:07:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想 我可以帮你把它们都烧毁\NIf you want, I can help you burn it all down.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.44,1:07:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,拜 乔纳森\NBye, Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.40,1:08:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.36,1:08:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这幢漂亮的老房子\NThis beautiful old house...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.60,1:08:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.76,1:08:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你见到乔纳森了吗\NDid you see Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.80,1:08:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.12,1:10:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你有烟吗\NDo you have a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.52,1:10:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你有孩子吗\NDo you have children?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.40,1:11:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我发觉有些欣慰的是你不想和我睡觉\NI find it comforting that you don't want to sleep with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.56,1:11:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那还能做什么\NWhat else then?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.08,1:11:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,噢是啊 没了\NOh, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.76,1:12:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,夜晚啊\NEvening.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.48,1:12:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你见到乔纳森了吗 - 没\NDid you see Jonathan? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.12,1:12:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像恶意纵火\NLooks like malicious arson.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.16,1:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,赫尔穆特在哪儿\NWhere is Helmut?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.60,1:12:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,赫尔穆特\NHelmut!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.20,1:12:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿 - 迷路了吗\NHello! - Did you get lost?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.36,1:12:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,出来吧 赫尔穆特 - 乔纳森\NCome on, Helmut! - Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.88,1:12:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,赫尔穆特\NHelmut!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.88,1:13:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我可以拿回夹克吗\NSay, could I have the jacket back?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.64,1:13:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是特供的一件 - 当然\NIt's an individual piece. - Sure!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.48,1:13:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拜\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.52,1:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拜\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.60,1:13:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 人来了\NOh, man...
